com.sails.map.overlay

Interface OverlayItem

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Circle, MapJPGOverlay, Marker, OrientationMarker, Polygon, Polyline, SingleLine, TextOverlay

    public interface OverlayItem
    An OverlayItem is a geographical object which can draw itself on a android.graphics.Canvas.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean draw(BoundingBox boundingBox, byte zoomLevel, Canvas canvas, Point canvasPosition, int centerX, int centerY, float rotationAngle)
      Draws this OverlayItem on the given canvas.

    • Method Detail

      • draw

        boolean draw(BoundingBox boundingBox,
           byte zoomLevel,
           Canvas canvas,
           Point canvasPosition,
           int centerX,
           int centerY,
           float rotationAngle)
        Draws this OverlayItem on the given canvas.
        Parameters:
        boundingBox - the geographical area which should be drawn.
        zoomLevel - the zoom level at which this OverlayItem should draw itself.
        canvas - the canvas on which this OverlayItem should draw itself.
        canvasPosition - the top-left pixel position of the canvas on the world map at the given zoom level.
        Returns:
        true if this OverlayItem is visible and has drawn itself, false otherwise.
